<center><font size=7><b>TLL (Tornado Low Level)</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 3</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>
To use a Kempston joystick you must first Merge in the Basic loader and then
edit the following lines. Remember that there's some degradation in sound
quality when using this method but 'you pays yer money and yer takes yer
choice!'
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
20 DATA
55,62,255,221,33,0,64,17,156,191,205,86,5,33,179,255,17,198,118,1,3,0,237,176,
        33,182,255,17,210,132,1,5,0,237,176,201,0,0,0,205,105,254,24,63
50 FOR N=65423 TO 65466
3000 RANDOMIZE USR 65423
</pre>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><a href="http://www.users.globalnet.co.uk/~jimg/yr08/yr08_43.htm#Hacker">http://www.users.globalnet.co.uk/~jimg/yr08/yr08_43.htm#Hacker</a>&nbsp; <i>(Dave Nicholls in Your Spectrum issue 08)</i> 

<br><hr>
To get infinite lives and time, Merge the program and stop the tape when you get
the OK message. Now list the Basic loader and edit lines 20,50 and 3000 to match
the lines shown below. Now type Run and start the tape from where you left off.
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;20 DATA 55,62,255,221,33,0,64,17,156,191,205,86,5,62,0,50,190,136,50,15,132,201
50 FOR N=65423 TO 65444
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3000 RANDOMIZE USR 65423
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
